Description: Petrolia SE, formerly Petrolia E&P Holdings SE, is a Cyprus-based company active within the oil and gas industry. It operates three business segments, namely Oil & Gas, Drilling & Well Technology and Oilfield Services. The Company is present in Norway, the Netherlands, Romania, Australia, New Zealand and Singapore. Its product categories comprise tubing, drill pipe, casing and handling equipment, as well as oilfield services. As of December 31, 2011, the Company had a number of subsidiaries, such as Petrolia Tool Pool AS, Petrolia Invest AS, Venture Drilling AS, Petrolia Drilling Ltd, Petrolia Norway AS, Petrolia Rigs II AS and Petrolia Drilling II AS, among others. The Company changed its name on February 4, 2013.
